description: A sample clip from an interview with Herbie Hancock.  Herbie shares his thoughts on Jaco Pastorius for the documentary film entitled, "JACO"… produced by Robert Trujillo of Metallica.  Remember to PLEDGE your support (http://www.pledgemusic.com/projects/jacothefilm) and subscribe to this channel.
